cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper deals with the creation of concept hierarchy from textual data, which falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the extraction of semantic information, which can be related to machine learning (cs.LG) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
